.rule_232_set_ip_address_for_ntp_server:


    Reference:    1. http://www.cisco.com/en/US/docs/ios-xml/ios/bsm/command/bsm-cr- n1.html#GUID-255145EB-D656-43F0-B361-D9CBCC794112 2. https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/td/docs/ios-xml/ios/bsm/command/bsm-cr-book/bsm-cr-n1.html#wp3294676008


    Remediation:  Configure at least one external NTP Server using the following commands
                  hostname(config)#ntp server {ntp-server_ip_address}
                   or
                  hostname(config)#ntp server {ntp server vrf [vrf name] ip address}

